    Preheading  Image with Text Overlay  Additional info in the subheading  Button 1 Button 2

  × Dr. Rebecca Marcus  Dr. Rebecca Marcus is a board-certified dermatologist with nearly two decades of experience specializing in medical, surgical and cosmetic dermatology. Her passion for skincare began at an early age when she would create homemade beauty products for her friends, searching for skincare that was both effective and uplifting. After years of study, culminating in residency training and a clinical research fellowship at Columbia University, Dr. Marcus was able to fulfill her dream of helping patients to love, appreciate and feel great in their own skin. True to her belief that skincare should make a person feel beautiful inside and out, Dr. Marcus set out to create Maei MD, a line of extremely effective and nurturing skincare products that people can understand and trust. 



       OUR PROMISE  “Helping people to feel beautiful and confident in their own skin is my passion. After years of research, I developed Serum 6, a singular superstar product combining the highest-quality, most essential ingredients for healthy, youthful, radiant skin. Maei MD is all about easy-to-use, high performance, nourishing skincare that delivers transformative results for body and spirit.”  - Dr. Rebecca Marcus, Founder of Maei MD  More about Maei MD

After years of study, culminating in residency training and a clinical research fellowship at Columbia University, Dr. Marcus was able to fulfill her dream of helping patients to love, appreciate and feel great in their own skin. True to her belief that skincare should make a person feel beautiful inside and out, Dr. Marcus set out to create Maei MD, a line of extremely effective and nurturing skincare products that people can understand and trust.
